package system.services.vucm


// The VUCM orchestrator process: the fleet ingress (VucmGate) + the campaign
// state machine (VucmCampaign). VucmTester is probe-only (NOT a composition
// member). Mirrors ucm (UcmGate+UcmFsm) / sm (SmGate+SmDaemon) / phm
// (PhmGate+PhmFsm). VUCM decides WHAT; it drives UCM (the HOW layer) over to_ucm.
composition Vucm {
    prototype VucmGate     vucm_gate
    prototype VucmCampaign vucm_campaign
}
